{"tid":493354,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)龍捲風 叛諜狂花 鄧寇克大行動","createTime":"2017-12-08T12:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T12:58:32.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29fe16f1d7b3783430f7a3347b5fd32850899e4a","tid":493354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=XOwmgkNIqoyGEiS1u1KBVf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1535b30e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=XOwmgkNIqoyGEiS1u1KBVf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=830afe97\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/a5/Twistermovieposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fa%2Fa5%2FTwistermovieposter.jpg&h=9b391196&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/52/Salt_film_theatrical_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F52%2FSalt_film_theatrical_poster.jpg&h=5a9ac179&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/86/Dunkirk_2017_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F86%2FDunkirk_2017_Poster.jpg&h=41886746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在美國的中部俄克拉何馬州。該州發生了半世紀以來罕見的暴風雨，一股破壞力極強的龍捲風正在醞釀形成中，隨時會吹襲該州，對該州的人命和財產構成威脅。面對該股龍捲風的來臨，該州的各個部門都嚴陣以待，計劃追蹤這場龍捲風的詭異路線，希望能夠率先解開該龍捲風之謎。<br />\n不久，破壞力驚人的龍捲風終於出現了，它以時速300哩正面吹襲俄克拉何馬州，當地房屋被龍捲風吹起，牛隻在空中旋轉，拖拉機像雨點落下，重型運油車變成空降炸彈&hellip;&hellip;為了搜集有關龍捲風數據，改善警告系統，一眾科學家不惜駕車，決定近距離接觸和追蹤龍捲風，並將電子感應器擺放在龍捲風的風眼裡當實驗，過程極為艱險。一場追蹤龍捲風的行動即將展開..<br />\n<br />\n2.劇情描述美國中情局特務探員「伊芙&middot;莎特」（安潔莉娜&middot;裘莉飾）自小由前蘇聯在冷戰時期，以地獄式訓練，培養出來的臥底刺客，本名「娜塔莎&middot;宣科夫」。莎特一直潛伏在CIA，為的是籌劃已久的毀滅美國華府的「DAY X」！後來被同為俄羅斯派往CIA的內奸揭發，俄國的情報頭子更把她心愛的丈夫抓去；莎特逼於無奈要叛逃，接下任務，擊潰白宮！然而，莎特又是否真的已重現俄諜的冷酷本性，還是另有內情？<br />\n<br />\n3.故事講述在第二次世界大戰期間，由英國、比利時、加拿大和法國所組成的盟軍被德國陸軍包圍在敦克爾克的海灘上，迫使英軍下令將士兵們撤退..<br />\n<br />\n8 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=XOwmgkNIqoyGEiS1u1KBVf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f0e4fe02\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=XOwmgkNIqoyGEiS1u1KBVf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=46dd84bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92e58c5b2397042e6f7d066f0b28a338b5e5d98","tid":493354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7b7e5b8b6881d75e98b3a769595325cbdda609","tid":493354,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:5